      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "RIBERY (4) stalked the lead after a clean break from the tricky draw and went on to finish second (23.03) at this track in a Special conditions race over 400m. Good form should continue. WATCH AND SEE (8) is a first starter from the Donald Turner kennel by Shima Shine out of Under Siege. Start all important and will need some luck getting across from the wide draw. Expected to be well fancied and can make an immediate impact. WIZARD WARRIOR (2) hasn't been far away, finishing in the money twice in a row including last time in a Maiden at Angle Park over 342m. Well placed here and should do much better. NOT THE GRAVY (7) placed last time out so worth considering.",
